headline: eBay Launches Auction of Pre-Loved Fashion and Custom Porsche Ahead of Miami Race Weekend
summary: Today, eBay announces an exclusive auction featuring a selection of pre-loved luxury fashion and a customized 1993 Porsche 911 Carrera 4 Cabriolet, timed to Miami's race weekend. Curated in collaboration with model and motorsport enthusiast Winnie Harlow, the auction spotlights the connection between fashion, motorsport culture, and eBay's marketplace for rare and one-of-a-kind finds. Bidding is open now through May 12 at ebay.com/guaranteedfitdrop.
